 54	 * form only carries the fields it renders; every unedited deep field (long bios,
 55	 * `Option` registration windows, image keys) survives, and the merged result is
 56	 * Schema-decoded at the single boundary before it is stored
 57	 * (`boundary-discipline`, `make-impossible-states-unrepresentable`).
