288	 * A per-image uploader. It posts to this route's action independently of the
289	 * surrounding save/publish form via a `useFetcher` — *not* a nested `<form>`
290	 * (HTML forbids nesting forms, and the editor's main `<Form>` wraps every
291	 * section, so rendering an inner form here would let SSR/hydration close or drop
292	 * either form's tags and silently break submission). Instead the uploader is a
293	 * plain element tree; the "Upload" button hands a one-off `FormData` (carrying
294	 * `intent=upload:<keyPath>` and the chosen `file`) to `fetcher.submit` as
