367	 * exactly like `ImageUpload` — *not* a nested `<form>` (the editor's main
368	 * `<Form>` wraps every section, and HTML forbids nested forms). The button
369	 * builds a one-off `FormData` carrying `intent=list-op` and the
370	 * `list:<path>:<kind>` control field, hands it to `fetcher.submit`, and the
371	 * action applies the op and redirects, revalidating the loader so the changed
372	 * list re-renders.
