374	 * The `value` carries the op payload: an item `id` for add/remove, or the
375	 * comma-joined surviving ids for a reorder. An "Add" mints a fresh `ListItemId`
376	 * client-side so the appended item's id is known before submit; the server
377	 * appends an item carrying only that id (draft-valid, publish-invalid until
378	 * edited).
